==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Psychophysics
<hw>Psy`cho*phys"ics</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<ety>[<ets>Psycho-</ets> + <ets>physics</ets>.]</ety> <def>The science
of the connection between nerve action and consciousness; the science
which treats of the relations of the psychical and physical in their
conjoint operation in man; the doctrine of the relation of function or
dependence between body and soul.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Psychopomp</ent>⟦br⟧
